repaq
------------------------------------------
A tool to compress FASTQ files with ultra-high compression ratio and high
speed. repaq supports compressing the FASTQ to .rfq or .rfq.xz formats.
Compressing to .rfq is ultra fast, while compressing to .rfq.xz provides very
high compression ratio.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libgcc1-14.4.0-1
  libstdc++6-14.4.0-1
  zlib0-1.3.2-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-14.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-14.4.0-1
  make-4.4.1-2
  zlib-devel-1.3.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/OpenGene/repaq

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/OpenGene/repaq/archive/refs/tags/v0.5.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack repaq-0.5.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./repaq-0.5.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/repaq-0.5.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/repaq-0.5.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(repaq)
  /usr/bin/repaq.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/repaq.README
  /usr/share/doc/repaq/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/repaq/README.md

